# Assignment No 05:  Calculate Volume of a sphere

radius = float(input("Enter Radius of Sphere: "))
vol = (4 * 22 * radius * radius * radius) / (3 * 7)

print("Volume of the Sphere with Radius", radius, "is", vol)

